Hi, we are stuck with setting up pathplanner, here is where we are in implementing it. We have generated code for our swerve with tuner x, made sure to add all of the CTRE pathplanner implementation lines that aren’t generated, added pathplannerlib, installed pathplanner, and licensed our CTRE devices. We have went the code to the robot but it is getting stuck on the section of Commandswervedrivetrain where it actually sets up the autochooser, and throwing an error along the lines of “failed to instantiate robot/pathplanner”. It will throw this error and then restart the robot over and over again, never actually reaching the point where the robot fully starts up and becomes usable. Does anyone have any insight into how to fix this? I will add code as soon as I get the chance.
